{"tid":2004082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] ZA 虛擬銀行騙局","createTime":"2020-05-06T08:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T20:35:46.000Z","uid":316066,"like":137,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"6b078f6bc925078a439b2b8a84acb483e4b352c2","tid":2004082,"uid":316066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"大家小心 ZA 網上虛擬銀行嘅騙局<br />\n最近網上成日賣廣告，話出咗香港首間虛擬銀行<br />\n<br />\n驗證嘅時候除左需要提供身份證之外，<br />\n仲要你前後左右唔同角度咁樣影自己個樣，<br />\n同埋要你做口部開合嘅動作。<br />\n<br />\n話就話係驗證係唔係真人，<br />\n但係拎外國既網上銀行 <a href=\"http://tide.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftide.co&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=d5643624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tide.co</a> 嚟做比較<br />\n人地淨係需要直接正面影一張相<br />\n並無需要多角度去拍攝<br />\n<br />\n而依家 ZA Bank 佢要求既多角度拍攝，<br />\n絕對可以完全記錄曬你嘅輪廓資料<br />\n從而配合智能燈柱嘅人面識別系統<br />\n幫助政府更新佢哋嘅資料庫，<br />\n從以前身份證嘅平面照片，升級為 3D 識別<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家唔好為左佢果少少優惠，出賣自己既個人資料"},{"pid":"2d8c6761cd7d00aa573c235c8d09e7973ca3f6eb","tid":2004082,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a74398e44c62342ab4b44d15cbf7203a290351f2","tid":2004082,"uid":62731,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"支那野不了"},{"pid":"636855da5e3bd42912cf1aa789940eb16ae64294","tid":2004082,"uid":51701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"眾安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ef887da73c281529305d16260691a275fc1b58","tid":2004082,"uid":316066,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"636855da5e3bd42912cf1aa789940eb16ae64294","tid":2004082,"uid":51701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"眾安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.g